    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">Dear esteemed colleague,</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">It is with great pleasure that we invite you to participate in the <strong>22nd International Electoral Awards &amp; Symposium</strong>, jointly hosted by the <strong>International Centre for Parliamentary Studies (ICPS)</strong> and the <strong>Commission on Elections of the Philippines (COMELEC)</strong>.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">This distinguished event will take place at <strong>The Manila Hotel, Philippines</strong> from <strong>Sunday 29th November to Thursday 3rd December 2026</strong>, bringing together electoral leaders, professionals, and innovators from across the globe to share knowledge, recognise achievements, and engage in high-level discussions on the future of electoral management.</p>

    <!-- Key details box -->
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 24px 0; background-color:#f0f4f8; border-radius:6px; border-left:4px solid #1a2744;">
    <tr><td style="padding: 20px 24px;">
        <p style="margin:0 0 4px; color:#1a2744; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px;">Key Details</p>
        <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top:10px;">
            <tr>
                <td style="padding:4px 16px 4px 0; color:#666; font-size:14px; vertical-align:top; white-space:nowrap;"><strong>Dates:</strong></td>
