    <!-- Programme overview -->
    <p style="margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a2744; font-size:16px; font-weight:700;">Programme at a Glance</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">The five-day programme includes a cultural tour, two days of symposium sessions with keynote presentations, panel discussions, fringe demonstrations, and networking opportunities. The event will culminate in the prestigious International Electoral Awards Ceremony, honouring excellence and innovation in electoral administration.</p>

